{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 10,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 334.937,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 4.923,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, proceed to give a record upon these plates",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 5.103,
      "end": 7.843,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of my proceedings, and my reign and ministry;",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 8.023,
      "end": 10.252,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, to proceed with my record,",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 10.432,
      "end": 13.311,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I must speak somewhat of the things of my father,",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 13.491,
      "end": 15.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also of my brothers.",
      "verse": "10:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 15.889,
      "end": 21.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, then after my father had made an end of speaking the words of his dream,",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 21.317,
      "end": 24.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also of exhorting them to all diligence,",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 24.562,
      "end": 26.93,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he spoke to them concerning the Jews\u2014",
      "verse": "10:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 27.61,
      "end": 29.746,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "That after they should be destroyed,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 29.926,
      "end": 32.109,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even that great city Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 32.289,
      "end": 35.493,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and many be carried away captive into Babylon,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 35.673,
      "end": 38.32,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the own due time of the Lord,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 38.5,
      "end": 40.079,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should return again,",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 40.259,
      "end": 43.603,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even be brought back out of captivity;",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 43.783,
      "end": 46.848,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after they should be brought back out of captivity",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 47.028,
      "end": 50.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should possess again the land of their inheritance.",
      "verse": "10:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 51.052,
      "end": 53.142,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, even six hundred years",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 53.322,
      "end": 56.155,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time that my father left Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 56.335,
      "end": 59.493,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a prophet would the Lord God raise up among the Jews\u2014",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 59.673,
      "end": 60.973,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even a Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 61.153,
      "end": 62.686,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or, in other words,",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 62.866,
      "end": 64.538,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a Savior of the world.",
      "verse": "10:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 65.218,
      "end": 67.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also spoke concerning the prophets,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 67.72,
      "end": 70.599,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "how great a number had testified of these things,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 70.779,
      "end": 72.497,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning this Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 72.677,
      "end": 74.349,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of whom he had spoken,",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 74.529,
      "end": 76.433,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or this Redeemer of the world.",
      "verse": "10:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 77.113,
      "end": 80.875,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, all mankind were in a lost and in a fallen state,",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 81.055,
      "end": 82.588,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ever would be",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 82.768,
      "end": 84.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save they should rely on this Redeemer.",
      "verse": "10:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 85.677,
      "end": 88.138,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spoke also concerning a prophet",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 88.318,
      "end": 90.594,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who should come before the Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 90.774,
      "end": 92.678,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to prepare the way of the Lord\u2014",
      "verse": "10:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 93.358,
      "end": 96.887,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, even he should go forth and cry in the wilderness:",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 97.067,
      "end": 99.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Prepare you the way of the Lord,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 99.244,
      "end": 101.102,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and make his paths straight;",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 101.282,
      "end": 104.44,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for there stands one among you whom you know not;",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 104.62,
      "end": 106.431,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he is mightier than I,",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 106.611,
      "end": 109.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose shoe's strap I am not worthy to unloose.",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 109.902,
      "end": 112.781,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And much spoke my father concerning this thing.",
      "verse": "10:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 113.461,
      "end": 117.594,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my father said he should baptize in Bethabara, beyond Jordan;",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 117.774,
      "end": 120.468,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he also said he should baptize with water;",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 120.648,
      "end": 123.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even that he should baptize the Messiah with water.",
      "verse": "10:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 124.3,
      "end": 127.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after he had baptized the Messiah with water,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 127.22,
      "end": 129.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he should behold and bear record",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 129.49,
      "end": 131.998,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he had baptized the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 132.178,
      "end": 134.825,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who should take away the sins of the world.",
      "verse": "10:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 135.505,
      "end": 138.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after my father had spoken these words",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 138.425,
      "end": 141.119,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he spoke to my brothers concerning the gospel",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 141.299,
      "end": 143.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which should be preached among the Jews,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 143.94,
      "end": 147.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also concerning the dwindling of the Jews in unbelief.",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 147.371,
      "end": 149.693,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had killed the Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 149.873,
      "end": 150.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who should come,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 151.168,
      "end": 153.026,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after he had been killed",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 153.206,
      "end": 154.924,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he should rise from the dead,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 155.104,
      "end": 157.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and should make himself manifest,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 157.56,
      "end": 158.953,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 159.133,
      "end": 160.619,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "10:11",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 161.299,
      "end": 164.828,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Indeed, even my father spoke much concerning the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 165.008,
      "end": 167.748,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also concerning the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 167.928,
      "end": 170.947,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they should be compared like to an olive tree,",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 171.127,
      "end": 173.774,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose branches should be broken off",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 173.954,
      "end": 177.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and should be scattered upon all the face of the earth.",
      "verse": "10:12",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 178.117,
      "end": 180.114,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, he said it must needs be",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 180.294,
      "end": 184.752,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we should be led with one accord into the land of promise,",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 184.932,
      "end": 187.718,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the fulfilling of the word of the Lord,",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 187.898,
      "end": 191.706,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we should be scattered upon all the face of the earth.",
      "verse": "10:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 192.386,
      "end": 195.219,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after the house of Israel should be scattered",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 195.399,
      "end": 197.814,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should be gathered together again;",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 197.994,
      "end": 199.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or, in other words,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 199.707,
      "end": 203.004,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the Gentiles had received the fullness of the Gospel,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 203.184,
      "end": 205.692,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the natural branches of the olive tree,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 205.872,
      "end": 208.194,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or the remnants of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 208.374,
      "end": 210.046,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should be grafted in,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 210.226,
      "end": 213.059,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or come to the knowledge of the true Messiah,",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 213.239,
      "end": 215.329,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their Lord and their Redeemer.",
      "verse": "10:14",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 216.009,
      "end": 218.285,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner of language",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 218.465,
      "end": 221.344,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did my father prophesy and speak to my brothers",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 221.524,
      "end": 223.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many more things",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 223.515,
      "end": 225.791,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I do not write in this book;",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 225.971,
      "end": 231.172,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have written as many of them as were expedient for me in my other book.",
      "verse": "10:15",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 231.852,
      "end": 234.731,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all these things, of which I have spoken,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 234.911,
      "end": 237.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "were done as my father dwelt in a tent,",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 237.552,
      "end": 239.224,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the valley of Lemuel.",
      "verse": "10:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 239.904,
      "end": 241.622,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I, Nephi,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 241.802,
      "end": 244.217,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having heard all the words of my father,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 244.397,
      "end": 247.648,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the things which he saw in a vision,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 247.828,
      "end": 251.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the things which he spoke by the power of the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 251.77,
      "end": 254.974,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which power he received by faith on the Son of God\u2014",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 255.154,
      "end": 258.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Son of God was the Messiah who should come\u2014",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 258.353,
      "end": 260.861,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Nephi, was desirous also",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 261.041,
      "end": 264.57,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I might see, and hear, and know of these things,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 264.75,
      "end": 266.561,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the power of the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 266.741,
      "end": 268.599,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the gift of God",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 268.779,
      "end": 271.287,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to all those who diligently seek him,",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 271.467,
      "end": 272.953,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as well in times of old",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 273.133,
      "end": 277.266,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as in the time that he should manifest himself to the children of men.",
      "verse": "10:17",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 277.946,
      "end": 281.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he is the same yesterday, today, and forever;",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 281.516,
      "end": 284.024,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the way is prepared for all men",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 284.204,
      "end": 286.387,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the foundation of the world,",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 286.567,
      "end": 289.586,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they repent and come to him.",
      "verse": "10:18",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 290.266,
      "end": 293.099,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he that diligently seeks shall find;",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 293.279,
      "end": 296.344,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the mysteries of God shall be unfolded to them,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 296.524,
      "end": 298.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the power of the Holy Ghost,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 298.515,
      "end": 301.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as well in these times as in times of old,",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 301.435,
      "end": 304.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and as well in times of old as in times to come;",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 304.634,
      "end": 307.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, the course of the Lord is one eternal round.",
      "verse": "10:19",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 308.147,
      "end": 311.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore remember, O man, for all your doings",
      "verse": "10:20",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 311.392,
      "end": 313.76,
      "type": "line",
